OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPlenty of
OL,6,Flate sunshine to end the day. Dry
OL,7,Fovernight, with increasing amounts of
OL,8,Fcloud cover in the far east once more,
OL,9,Fwith some hill fog possible in places.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FMorning cloud clearing to
OL,12,Fleave another dry and sunny day. The
OL,13,Fsunshine turning hazy at times in the
OL,14,Fafternoon. Temperatures a little lower
OL,15,Fas winds turn northerly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
